{
  "stem": "20848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that's when he picked up the child and, and marched out very proudly with his head held high with the children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as I said, there was a lot of people who were taken that day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now I'm going to tell you something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Our next door neighbors was a young couple with a little girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's relevant, otherwise I wouldn't bring it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was an elderly couple that were the parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Like the parents, a daughter with her husband, and a little girl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And that day, the Germans took away the mother, the daughter, and the granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The men were not at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the men-- they were very, very friendly with my parents, the whole family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the men apparently, were very wealthy people who had timber yards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they had-- they were-- had a lot of German friends and German-- before the war-- German customers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And when they took away the, the wives and the child, when they came home and saw it, they became absolutely frantic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they got in touch with the German clients.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I know it all from my parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I didn't know it at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they got hold of the German clients, and they offered an enormous amount of money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "First of all, they said follow, follow what happened to, to, to, to the wives, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because they were put on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the car followed the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "With the Germans followed the, the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they were, you know, authorized to offer an enormous amount of money to get those women back, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Like the, you know, the mother and the daughter and the granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The-- I think the granddaughter was, at the time, a little girl, maybe three or four years old.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
